title: Ethereum ($ETH), $XRP, and Solana ($SOL) Lead the Way as Altcoin Season Looms
description: At a time in which the flagship cryptocurrency’s dominance of the market appears to be dwindling, several altcoins have been showing signs of progress, with Ethereum ($ETH), $XRP, and Solana ($SOL) all moving upward over the last few days. Such a shift in the crypto landscape suggests that a new altcoin season could be on […]
